This coverage was created using locations listed in the AFO database and registrations submitted as part of the Iowa Plan.   All registrations in the Iowa Plan were voluntary.  Animal units were generally assigned as reported on registrations and construction permit applications, however, some numbers were modified based on Statement of Intent forms or site visits.  Animal numbers should only be used as estimates.  No quality control procedures were used to verify these animal numbers.  The information contained in this coverage was developed from November, 2006, to March, 2007, therefore, any changes that were made to the AFO database during that time may not have been included.  52 operations were not mapped either because there was insufficient location information or because they were suspected to be duplicates of mapped operations.</abstract>    <purpose>This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.</purpose>    <langdata Sync="TRUE">en</langdata></descript>   <timeperd>    <timeinfo>     <sngdate>      <caldate>20120817</caldate>     </sngdate>    </timeinfo>    <current>ground condition</current>   </timeperd>   <status>    <progress>Complete</progress>    <update>As needed</update>   </status>   <spdom>    <bounding>     <westbc Sync="TRUE">-96.596562</westbc>     <eastbc Sync="TRUE">-90.136627</eastbc>     <northbc Sync="TRUE">43.553032</northbc>     <southbc Sync="TRUE">40.536334</southbc>    </bounding>    <lboundng><leftbc Sync="TRUE">209211.000000</leftbc><rightbc Sync="TRUE">731427.000000</rightbc><bottombc Sync="TRUE">4492954.000000</bottombc><topbc Sync="TRUE">4822231.000000</topbc></lboundng></spdom>   <keywords>    <theme>     <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Category</themekt>     <themekey>farming</themekey>    </theme>    <theme>     <themekt>None</themekt>     <themekey>open feeldlots</themekey>     <themekey>cattle</themekey>    </theme>    <place>     <placekt>GNIS</placekt>     <placekey>Iowa</placekey>    </place>   </keywords>   <accconst>None</accconst>   <useconst> The development of the coverages in the NRGIS Library represents a major investment of staff time and effort.
